{"tid":1835980,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"已經準備迎接手持午餐肉就可以有西屌的日子","createTime":"2020-01-23T04:58:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T10:37:50.000Z","uid":68026,"like":27,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"658b832e59e851887dea758036e3408b4d9cb7e1","tid":1835980,"uid":68026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T04:58:31.000Z","msg":"WWIII又好,武漢肺炎又好,共產黨打到黎又好,有咩事發生都唔驚,,要鳩縮唔出街都實有得食~~<br />\n當然,,到有日真係出現 全香港範圍MAP炮 就咩都唔使<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/163932_a2cdc25e37dba43ebb1f73f9ef75e4e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F163932_a2cdc25e37dba43ebb1f73f9ef75e4e1.jpg&h=fc554873&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n放在廚房櫃的鑵頭同米,[現鑵頭總存貨有$10000左右]米有50kg<br />\n由歐洲火腿,到中國午餐肉,回煱肉,,豆,菜,金寶湯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3dHRiV5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3dHRiV5.jpg&h=bb698acb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一箱箱未開太多,,放到出廳[依d全部係魚]<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/164003_45a6f56b9383021925f49be7d93c4258.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F164003_45a6f56b9383021925f49be7d93c4258.jpg&h=61f1bb56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n水污染,未驚~~~現有16箱 1.5L X12<br />\n其實一向飲樽裝水好耐,現在D水喉水煮完都飲到唔舒服<br />\n即食面 有 5箱左右啦<br />\n<br />\n另外,,打邊爐石油氣有存貨 21支,,<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n來吧~~~<br />\n大混亂~~~<br />\n特大災難~~~<br />\n無水~~無電~~無野買的日子呀~~~<br />\n<br />\n期待,手持午餐肉就可以有西屌的日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98b113ed0a13ce13f3295669d4242d58be218470","tid":1835980,"uid":119875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T05:03:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾多年"},{"pid":"3fcdc50dad71e02012763ad5e3e554b6abd12f4c","tid":1835980,"uid":98291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T06:21:30.000Z","msg":"有冇20年?"},{"pid":"663ad4ae2e9b1e842b6fc6379c42d8637e764ed1","tid":1835980,"uid":137604,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T06:52:48.000Z","msg":"想睇真心膠覆你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81ef907bf0cc4f3cdcb56805423bf7ee92ba4856","tid":1835980,"uid":223399,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T07:02:13.000Z","msg":"我有武漢肺炎<br />\n可唔可以幫你含"},{"pid":"cdf675d33f328051677366a1b5db1636fd884a5a","tid":1835980,"uid":237830,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T07:05:32.000Z","msg":"之前先話支那用豬瘟肉做午餐肉<br />\n而家樓豬儲中國午餐肉<br />\n真係傻豬豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6fc88a0f8bebd086cff266c1353c40c73063f8e","tid":1835980,"uid":193251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T07:14:29.000Z","msg":"依家係手持口罩有閪屌啦"},{"pid":"9829c75501212babc5c8e10ac016573080a23862","tid":1835980,"uid":191139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T07:17:25.000Z","msg":"想幫你含"},{"pid":"62d97812268af9253c486e14fc4aa968a9608a3b","tid":1835980,"uid":319806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T07:18:31.000Z","msg":"50kg米&hellip;小心生穀牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99e1abe4a7609dd5fddfc9851e10fbd000ab0240","t